profile_summary:
Joel Sen is a skilled software developer with a strong background in leveraging cutting-edge technologies to build innovative solutions. With a solid foundation in Python, SCSS, and HTML, Joel possesses a unique combination of technical skills that enable him to efficiently design and develop high-quality applications. 

As a forward-thinking developer with a passion for "making things," Joel's creativity and technical expertise have earned him a reputation as a reliable and results-driven professional. With a growing network of peers and a portfolio of 13 public repositories, Joel continues to demonstrate his commitment to staying at the forefront of industry trends and best practices.
